p: SUBPOENA Territory of Washington County of Spokane}ss TO John Mabine, Mose, Ruby Paul Killinger, Summer A. Chandle. In the name of the United States you are hereby required to appear before the undersigned, one of the Justices of the Peace in and for the said County, on the 29th day of June 1886, at 10 o'clock A.M. at his office in Spokane Falls W.T. to give evidence in a certain cause then and there to be tried between the Territory of Washington Plaintiff and Ray Raymond Defendant On the part of the The Territory of WashingtonDefendant Given under my hand this 28th day of June 1886 J.J.L. Peel Justice of the Peace
